**Session Zero Checklist**

*Complete these before your first session. Check each item once done.*

- Answer the three Step I questions (What do you want? / What have you lost? / What does the Loom want?)

- Choose your Kindred and note your Vitality Die and Attribute bonuses (Step II)

- Choose your Path and note your Vitality Die and core resource (Step III)

- Generate Resonance Attributes using one of the three methods (Step IV)

- Roll your Fate Number (1d20), Primal Essence (1d6: 1=Alpha, 2-5=Beta, 6=Omega), and Zodiac Sign (Step V)

- Choose your Origin and note your Disciplines, tool, language, and Origin Feature (Step VI)

- Record your Depth 1 Path features, Vitality, Guard Rating, and core resource maximum (Step VII)

- Choose your starting equipment package or take starting Gold Marks (Step VIII)

- Confirm your Kindred-Zodiac Resonance ability with the Game Master (Session Zero conversation)

- Write your three Narrative Hooks on your character sheet and share them with the table (Step IX)

