| **Domain Discipline Mastery** | Depth 1 | Each Zodiac Priest gains Mastery in two Disciplines determined by their sign's domain. These Disciplines always benefit from the domain's Aetheric enhancement — the Priest's connection to their sign amplifies even mundane application of these skills. Additionally: Zodiac Priests prepare their Workings from the full list of their sign's domain, plus the universal Priest list — they do not prepare individual Workings but rather have access to any Working in their domain at any time. The domain is always open to them. |
| **Legendary Beast Communion** | Depth 7 | The Zodiac Priest may attempt direct communion with their sign's Legendary Beast once per week — a 1-hour meditation ritual. The Beast is not controlled and may refuse. On a successful Attunement Active Resonance (Threshold 18, Resonant Fortune), the Priest receives one communication from the Beast — not language, but intention, image, and emotional weight. The Beast's cognitive state (confused, angry, serene, alert) is always clear; what it is responding to often requires interpretation. A Zodiac Priest who has achieved Depth 21 can communicate two-directionally — the Beast begins to respond to them specifically rather than simply broadcasting. |
| **Domain Embodiment** | Depth 17 | For 1 minute per Deep Attunement, the Zodiac Priest may fully embody their sign's domain force. During Embodiment: all Benediction effects double; all domain Workings cost no Aetheric Channels; the Priest's appearance shifts to reflect the domain (a Leo Priest's eyes become solar gold, a Scorpio Priest's shadow moves independently). Creatures witnessing Embodiment must make a Resonance Warding Resonance (Threshold 18) or be Dread-Struck for 1 Pulse — not from malice, but from proximity to a mortal fully expressing divine force. |

**Callings**

**♈ Aries Domain — Initiative ****&**** Primal Fire***  —  Fire Benediction*

Domain Benediction: All allies within 30 ft act before all enemies for the next Pulse, regardless of Pulse Order — the domain of initiative reshapes the moment of beginning.

Domain Workings include: Fireball variants, Haste, Divine Favor (fire-aspected), Flame Strike, Wall of Fire. All deal fire damage regardless of base type.

**♉ Taurus Domain — Endurance ****&**** Earthly Wealth***  —  Earth Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Touch the ground. A 30-ft radius becomes hallowed terrain — all allies within gain Resonant Fortune on Warding Resonances against being moved against their will for 24 hours.

Domain Workings include: Stoneskin, Earth Tremor, Spike Growth, Transmute Rock, Move Earth. Enhanced stability and geological force.

**♋ Cancer Domain — Protection ****&**** Sheltering***  —  Ward Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Create a sanctuary around one creature you touch. For 1 hour: all Strike Resonances against them have Resonant Discord; they have Resonant Fortune on all Warding Resonances. The shelter of the Adamant Crab, expressed through a mortal intermediary.

Domain Workings include: Shield of Faith, Sanctuary, Warding Bond, Aura of Protection (Vitality drain variant), Forcecage. All oriented toward keeping others safe.

**♌ Leo Domain — Heroism ****&**** Solar Light***  —  Solar Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Emanate solar light in a 30-ft radius for 1 minute. All Void-Husks and undead within take 3d8 radiant damage immediately. All allies gain temporary Vitality equal to your Attunement modifier and immunity to Dread-Struck for the duration.

Domain Workings include: Guiding Bolt, Daylight, Sunbeam, Wall of Light, Dawn. All deal radiant damage and suppress Void-energy in their area of effect.

**♍ Virgo Domain — Community ****&**** Purification***  —  Purification Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Purify a 30-ft radius. All Corrupted, Soul-Swayed, and Dread-Struck conditions are removed from all allies within. Ashen Coil blight-rot is suppressed for 24 hours. The Stygian Scorpion's Heart-Sting Toxin is neutralized completely.

Domain Workings include: Cure Wounds (enhanced), Lesser/Greater Restoration, Protection from Poison, Mass Healing Word, Heal. All restoration effects function at double potency.

**♎ Libra Domain — Divine Law ****&**** Balance***  —  Law Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Declare one action taken in this encounter unjust. The creature who took that action must make a Resonance Warding Resonance (Threshold 18) or be Resonance-Locked for 1 round — the domain of divine law refusing to allow the injustice to continue unchallenged.

Domain Workings include: Command, Zone of Truth, Hold Person/Monster, Banishment, Divine Word. All compel truthfulness or righteous constraint.

**♏ Scorpio Domain — Secrets ****&**** Transformation***  —  Death Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Touch a creature at 0 Vitality. They are stabilized and held in stasis for up to 24 hours — experiencing the threshold between life and death without crossing it. During stasis, they cannot be targeted by further effects and do not make Loom Tests. The Priest determines when stasis ends.

Domain Workings include: Inflict Wounds, Speak with Dead, Animate Dead (Sideros: temporary moral alignment required), Harm, Power Word Kill. All interact with the boundary between living and dead.

**♐ Sagittarius Domain — Exploration ****&**** Stars***  —  Horizon Benediction*

Domain Benediction: All allies within 30 ft gain 30 ft of additional movement speed for 1 minute and cannot be reduced below 1 movement speed by any effect. The domain of exploration refuses to let anything stop the journey.

Domain Workings include: Longstrider, Pass Without Trace, Far Step, Teleportation Circle, Plane Shift. All enhance range, reach, and the capacity to go where others cannot.

**♑ Capricorn Domain — Ambition ****&**** Mastery***  —  Mastery Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Grant one ally Mastery in any Discipline they can observe being used — permanently. The domain of mastery can compress years of practice into a moment of cosmic recognition. Usable once per week per recipient.

Domain Workings include: Enhance Ability, Skill Empowerment, Heroes' Feast, Foresight, Wish (limited to skill and capability enhancement). All enhance mortal capacity.

**♒ Aquarius Domain — Creation ****&**** Community***  —  Communion Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Create a Shared Resonance Field lasting 1 hour — all Bonded creatures within 60 ft may freely use each other's Aetheric Channels and Tapas Points as if they were their own. Resources flow between bond members without restriction.

Domain Workings include: Create Food and Water, Leomund's Tiny Hut, Telepathic Bond, Mass Cure Wounds, Temple of the Gods. All sustain and shelter communities.

**♓ Pisces Domain — Prophecy ****&**** Dreams***  —  Vision Benediction*

Domain Benediction: All creatures within 30 ft experience a 6-second prophetic vision simultaneously — the Game Master delivers one true image of an imminent threat or pivotal choice. All who receive the vision have Resonant Fortune on their next roll related to what they saw.

Domain Workings include: Augury, Divination, Dream, Foresight, True Seeing. All reveal what is hidden in time or the subconscious.

**♊ Gemini Domain — Duality ****&**** Knowledge***  —  Duality Benediction*

Domain Benediction: Split one Working's effect: cast any Priest Working and apply its full effect to two targets simultaneously at no additional Channel cost. The domain of duality extends what was one into two without diminishing either.

Domain Workings include: Identify, Detect Thoughts, Sending, Arcane Eye, Legend Lore. All gather, transmit, or process knowledge across distance or minds.

