**Solar Guard**

*Base: Fighter · Alpha/Beta-aspected · Vitality Die: d10*

**Core Mechanic:  **Surge of Will (replaces Second Wind + Action Surge)  Vitality Surge (Instinct, 1/Short or Deep Attunement): Restore Vitality equal to 1d10 + Resonance Depth. This is not magical healing — it is trained stress response. Works in anti-magic fields. Works in The Stillness. Will does not require the Aether. Combat Surge (Act, 2/Short or Deep Attunement — increases at higher Depths): On your Moment, you may take one additional Act. Not an Instinct — a full additional Act. Replaces Action Surge. A Solar Guard in Combat Surge can: attack twice and use an Instinct and still have an Act remaining. This represents trained efficiency reaching a point of genuine superhuman performance without cosmic aid. Fighting Discipline (chosen at Depth 1): Select one fighting tradition — Archery, Defense, Dueling

