| 2 | +2 | 10 | Fighting Style, Aether Smite, Oath Workings begin |
| **3** | +2 | 15 | Calling chosen, Oath Calling chosen (Solar Compact / Loom's Justice / Ancient Sideros), Calling D3 features |
| **4** | +2 | 20 | Attribute Score Improvement, Zodiac Attunement (after Legendary Beast encounter), — |
| **5** | +3 | 25 | Extra Strike, Calling D5 features |
| 6 | +3 | 30 | Aura of Oath (10 ft, allies add RES mod to Warding Resonances) |
| 7 | +3 | 35 | Calling D7 features |
| 8 | +3 | 40 | Attribute Score Improvement, — |
| **9** | +4 | 45 | Aura of Courage (allies immune to Dread-Struck within 10 ft) |
| 10 | +4 | 50 | Calling D10 features |
| 11 | +4 | 55 | Improved Aether Smite (+1d8 radiant on all melee hits) |
| 12 | +4 | 60 | Attribute Score Improvement, — |
