| 15 | +5 | 3 (max 5th) | Scion Boon #6, Mystic Arcanum: one 9th-tier Working/day |
| 16 | +5 | 3 (max 5th) | Attribute Score Improvement, Patron Invocations (+1 known) |
| **17** | +6 | 3 (max 5th) | — |
| 18 | +6 | 3 (max 5th) | Scion Boon #7 |
| 19 | +6 | 3 (max 5th) | Attribute Score Improvement, — |
