**Combat Quick Reference**

**Core Resonance Formulas**

| **Formula** | **Calculation** |
| --- | --- |
| **Strike Resonance (Attack)** | d20 + Attribute modifier + Mastery Bonus vs. target Guard Rating |
| **Warding Resonance (Save)** | d20 + Attribute modifier (+ MB if Path grants proficiency) |
| **Active Resonance (Skill Check)** | d20 + Attribute modifier + Mastery Bonus (if Mastered) |
| **Guard Rating -- Light/No Armor** | 10 + Swiftness modifier + armor bonus |
| **Guard Rating -- Unarmored Siddha** | 10 + Attunement modifier + Mastery Bonus (Tapas pool full) |
| **Guard Rating -- Gear-Forged** | 10 + Endurance modifier (constructed frame) |
| **Vitality (Depth 1)** | Roll Vitality Die + Endurance modifier (minimum 1) |
| **Vitality (each new Depth)** | Roll HD + END modifier; add to total. Use higher of Kindred or Path die. |
| **Ambient Attunement (Passive Perception)** | 10 + Attunement modifier + Mastery Bonus (if Perception Mastered) |
| **Working Threshold (Spell Save DC)** | 8 + Mastery Bonus + Weaving Attribute modifier |
| **Working Attack Bonus** | Mastery Bonus + Weaving Attribute modifier |

**Loom Tests (at 0 Vitality)**

| *Called **"**Death Saving Throws**"** in D**&**D. In Sideros the Loom of Fate holds the thread -- the world decides if it is time to cut it.* |
| --- |

| **Roll** | **Effect** |
| --- | --- |
| 10 or higher | Success -- record it. Three successes before three failures: stabilise at 0 Vitality. Stop making Loom Tests (remain unconscious). |
| 9 or lower | Failure -- record it. Three failures before three successes: thread ends. Character dies. |
| Natural 20 | Instant success AND regain 1 Vitality, regaining consciousness immediately. |
| Natural 1 | Counts as TWO failures. |
| Taking damage at 0 Vitality | Each damage instance = one failure. A critical hit = two failures. |
| Massive damage (full -> 0, excess > max Vitality) | Thread ends immediately. No Loom Tests. |
| **Fated Bond -- bonded partner within 30 ft** | Converts one Loom Test failure to a success per Pulse. The bond's weight on the Loom. |
| Stabilising a downed creature | Medicine Active Resonance DC 10 as an Act within 5 ft. Stops Loom Tests; creature unconscious. Regains 1 Vitality after 1d4 hours. |

**Warding Resonances -- Attribute Mapping**

| **Attribute** | **When Used** |
| --- | --- |
| **Forcefulness** | Athletic feats, being knocked back, crushing or physical force effects |
| **Swiftness** | Explosions, breath weapons, area effects -- anything that can be dodged |
| **Endurance** | Poison, disease, exhaustion, death effects, physical constitution |
| **Acuity** | Illusions, mind-affecting effects requiring logical resistance |
| **Attunement** | Charms, scrying, emotional manipulation, Aetheric influence |
| **Resonance** | Fear effects, social coercion, Fated Bond Active Resonances, Void corruption |

**Weapon Mastery Rules**

| **Status** | **Effect** |
| --- | --- |
| **Mastered** | Full Mastery Bonus on Strike Resonance attack AND damage rolls |
| **Half-Mastered** | Half Mastery Bonus (rounded down) on attack rolls only |
| **Unmastered** | Resonant Discord (2d20 take lower) on all Strike Resonances with this weapon |
| **Armor without Mastery** | Resonant Discord on all FOR + SWI Active Resonances and Warding Resonances |
| **Training to gain Mastery** | 250 gm + 250 days with an instructor willing to teach you (Downtime) |

**Aether-Dampening Ore -- The Stillness**

| *The Dunmarim Stone Kingdom and Republic of Argentum control Ore supply. The Coil deploys it tactically. Any encounter in a Stillness zone fundamentally changes the combat economy for Weave-capable characters.* |
| --- |

| **Element** | **Rule** |
| --- | --- |
| **Effect on Weave-capable characters** | Resonance-Locked -- cannot Weave Workings of any tier while within the suppression field |
| **Effect on Aetheric Artifacts** | Temporarily suppressed -- magical weapon bonuses inactive; Aether-enhanced armor loses enhancement |
| **Black Iron weapons** | Retain full effectiveness in the Stillness (non-Aetheric by nature). Treat as normal steel in standard environments, but unaffected by Ore suppression. |
| **Ashé-Medium abilities** | Partially suppressed -- Ashe is biological, not Aetheric. Core Vessel abilities persist; advanced Invocations that require active Aether are suppressed. |
| **Gear-Forged frames** | Partial suppression depending on Geode quality. Tier I Geodes: fully suppressed. Tier III+: 50% capacity. Frame Vitality still functions. |
| **Detecting Ore zones** | Weave-capable characters feel the suppression before entering (Ambient Attunement check DC 12). Te Kapo sense it through Void-adjacent perception. Stellar Cartographers cannot read Fate Numbers inside. |
| **Ore range** | Refined Ore: 30 ft radius per unit. Dunmarim-processed: 60 ft. Argent Spire-grade: 120 ft. Stacks -- do not overlap. |

**Combat Moment Structure**

| **Element** | **Description** |
| --- | --- |
| **Pulse Order** | d20 + Swiftness modifier each Pulse. Higher = act sooner. Resets every Pulse. |
| **Act (1/Moment)** | Strike, Weave, Grapple, Dash, Use Item, Help, Feat ability, and similar actions |
| **Instinct (1/Moment)** | Draw weapon, Path Instinct features, drink potion, unarmed strike, bonus-action equivalents |
| **Movement** | Up to Speed in feet; can split around Act. Not an action. |
| **Reflex (1/Pulse)** | Triggered reaction on another creature's Moment (Opportunity Strike, Dodge, Loom Test conversion) |
| **Resonant Fortune** | Roll 2d20, take higher. From Fated Bonds, Path features, Zodiac Feats, favourable conditions. |
| **Resonant Discord** | Roll 2d20, take lower. From unfavourable conditions, Unmastered weapons, Void exposure, Stillness. |

**Attunement Recovery**

| **Type** | **Time** | **What It Restores** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Brief Attunement** | 1 hour (no combat) | Spend and roll Vitality Dice (pool = Resonance Depth) + END modifier per die. Restores Brief Attunement resources: some Tapas (if meditative), Resonance Seeker Chord recovery, certain Instinct abilities. +1 Vitality Die if bonded partner within 10 ft. |
| **Deep Attunement** | 8 hours (includes sleep) | All Vitality restored. All Aetheric Channels restored. All Vitality Dice restored. All Tapas Points. Omote-Ura Gauge resets to clan default. Removes 1 Exhaustion level. Clears Aetheric Depletion. Clears 1 stack of Void-Touched Exposure (or use Weep-Stone to clear more). |

**Conditions Reference**

*All Sideros conditions with D**&**D equivalents, effects, and how they end. Conditions marked with a dagger (+) have no D**&**D equivalent.*

| **Condition** | **D****&****D Equiv.** | **Effect** | **Ends When** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Corrupted** | *Poisoned* | 1d6 damage at start of each Moment; Resonant Discord on attacks and skill checks | Successful END Warding Resonance (DC = source); purification Working or Weep-Stone |
| **Seized** | *Restrained* | Speed becomes 0 and cannot be increased | Source ends; successful FOR or SWI Active Resonance as Act (contest) |
| **Prone** | *Prone* | Resonant Fortune vs. melee Strike Resonances; Resonant Discord vs. ranged Strike Resonances | Stand up as part of movement (costs half Speed) |
| **Sight-Severed** | *Blinded* | Resonant Discord on attacks that require sight; creatures have Resonant Fortune vs. you | Source ends; duration expires |
| **Deafened** | *Deafened* | Fail hearing checks; immune to sonic effects; Resonance Seeker aura abilities blocked | Source ends; duration expires |
| **Grappled** | *Grappled* | Speed 0; Resonant Discord on Strike Resonances against targets other than grappler | Act: FOR or SWI Active Resonance contest vs. grappler; grappler releases; grappler incapacitated |
| **Exhausted** | *Exhaustion (6 levels)* | L1: Discord all Active Resonances / L2: Speed halved / L3: Discord all Strikes & Wardings / L4: Max Vitality halved / L5: Speed 0 / L6: Thread ends | Deep Attunement removes 1 level (requires food and water) |
| **Dread-Struck** | *Frightened* | Resonant Discord on everything while source is visible; cannot move toward source voluntarily | Source leaves sight; duration expires; successful RES Warding Resonance |
| **Soul-Swayed** | *Charmed* | Treats source as trusted ally; cannot make Strike Resonances against source | Source deals damage to creature; successful RES Warding Resonance; duration expires |
| **Dazed** | *Stunned (minor)* | Resonant Discord on all Resonances until start of creature's next Moment | Start of next Moment (automatic) |
| **Loom-Suspended** | *Unconscious* | Drop prone; lose Act and Instinct; auto-fail FOR + SWI Warding Resonances; attacks have Resonant Fortune; crits within 5 ft automatic | Any healing restoring Vitality; duration (some sources) |
| **Resonance-Locked** | *Incapacitated/Silenced* | Cannot Weave Workings or use Channel-requiring abilities | Leave Ore zone; source duration expires; Dispel Working |
| **Resonance-Shattered** | *None* | Resonance-Locked + Resonant Discord on ALL rolls + Fated Bond blocked (thread still exists, cannot flow) | Deep Attunement; 5th-tier Restoration Working |
| **Aetheric Depletion** | *None (5 levels)* | L1: Discord on Working rolls / L2: Half damage on Workings / L3: No Workings tier 3+ / L4: No Workings any tier / L5: 1d10 psychic damage per Moment | 1 level per Brief Attunement; all levels on Deep Attunement |
| **Void-Touched Exposure** | *None* | Per stack: Discord on Insight; directional awareness of Hollow Serpent. At 3+ stacks: Core begins reaching character (Game Master delivers intrusive thoughts). | Deep Attunement clears 1 stack; Weep-Stone (1 charge) clears 2 stacks; Kanya Siddha Purification ritual clears all stacks |
| **Loom-Tested** | *Dying* | 0 Vitality; make Loom Tests each turn (d20, DC 10). See Loom Tests table. Thread ends on 3 failures. | 3 successes = stable; natural 20 = regain 1 Vitality; Medicine DC 10 = stabilised |

*Conditions marked with a dagger are Sideros-original with no D**&**D equivalent. Red rows have unique Sideros mechanical significance.*

**Zodiac Attunement Feats**

*REQUIREMENTS: (1) Physical encounter with your sign's Beast within 300 ft -- the Beast must actively perceive you. (2) Survive with Fate Number intact -- Void-Touched Exposure during the encounter disqualifies. (3) Reach Resonance Depth 4.*

| **Rule** | **Detail** |
| --- | --- |
| **Banking the prerequisite** | You may encounter your Beast at D1 and bank the encounter. The feat unlocks at D4 as normal. The Bank cannot expire. |
| **Gear-Forged exception** | Receive Zodiac Attunement automatically at D1. The Resonant Geode heart IS the encounter. No Beast proximity required. |
| **Secondary Attunement (non-sign Beast)** | Surviving a non-sign Beast encounter grants ONE ability from that Beast's domain, usable once per Deep Attunement. This is a gift -- not trained toward. Beasts choose what they offer. |
| **Cross-Cultural Feat Variant (D8)** | After deep study of a second zodiac tradition (250 gm + 250 days minimum), a formalized version of Secondary Attunement becomes reliable once per Deep Attunement. Available at D8. |
| **Void-Touched numbers (13, 66, 99)** | Bond abilities operate at one tier higher than bond tier. Zodiac Attunement Feat functions normally but the Hollow Serpent's frequency is detectable by Stellar Cartographers behind the Number. |

| **Sign** | **Feat (Beast)** | **Passive Benefit** | **Active Ability (1x/Deep Att.)** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **♈ Aries** | **Mesha's Charge** **(Ashen Ram)** | Dash as Instinct once/Moment | On 20+ ft charge + melee hit: target makes FOR save DC 8+MB+FOR or knocked prone |
| **♉ Taurus** | **Khalkotauros's Endurance** **(Khalkotauros)** | +2 Vitality per current Depth, +2 each new Depth; count as one size larger for grappling | Once/Deep Attunement: drop to 1 Vitality instead of 0 |
| **♊ Gemini** | **Twin-Serpents' Duality** **(Twin-Serpents)** | Maintain 2 Sustained Resonance Workings simultaneously | Once/Deep Attunement: reroll any failed Active Resonance |
| **♋ Cancer** | **Adamant's Ward** **(Adamant Crab)** | Always know exact position of every creature within 30 ft (immune to invisibility defeat) | Reflex: Impose Resonant Discord on Strike Resonance targeting creature within 5 ft; attacker ATT save DC 12 or targets you instead |
| **♌ Leo** | **Nemean's Glory** **(Nemean Lion)** | Immune to Dread-Struck; attackers who use fear vs. you make RES save DC 8+MB+RES or become Dread-Struck of you for 1 min | On reducing creature to 0 Vitality: allies who see you gain temp Vitality = RES mod + Resonant Fortune on next Strike |
| **♍ Virgo** | **Queen Bee's Precision** **(Queen Bee)** | Diagnose any Aetheric curse, disease, or condition in 1 minute (source, progression, cure) | Once/Moment on dealing damage: add ATT modifier to damage; Help action grants Resonant Fortune on TWO rolls instead of one |
| **♎ Libra** | **Great Roc's Equilibrium** **(Great Roc)** | Roll within 3 of DC either way: may choose success with Game Master complication | Once/Deep Attunement: Binding Judgment — two creatures make a binding agreement for 1 hour (cannot act against it) |
| **♏ Scorpio** | **Stygian Revelation** **(Stygian Scorpion)** | Resonant Fortune on all Deception and Insight Active Resonances | Touch an object/location for 1 min: read its emotional history (Psychometry; not suppressible by Ore); on dealing damage: learn one piece of info the target is actively concealing |
| **♐ Sagittarius** | **Star-Stag's Horizon** **(Star-Metal Stag)** | Ranged Strike Resonances and Working attacks ignore all cover; +10 ft movement speed | Once/Deep Attunement: ask Game Master one factual question about a location you're traveling toward |
| **♑ Capricorn** | **Sea-Goat's Ascent** **(Sea-Goat)** | Climb speed = walk speed on any surface; when long-term goal declared at session start, Resonant Fortune on all related Active Resonances for that session | Climb any surface without Active Resonance (except extreme conditions) |
| **♒ Aquarius** | **Kelp-Weaver's Network** **(Kelp-Weaver)** | Maintain telepathic contact with up to 5 willing creatures simultaneously (same plane; no Sustained Resonance) | Broadcast to all simultaneously as Instinct |
| **♓ Pisces** | **Dream-Fish's Sight** **(Twin Dream-Fish)** | Communicate with sleeping creatures within 1 mile (as Dream Working; 1×/Deep, no Channel) | Once/Deep Attunement: prophetic trance — ask Game Master one yes/no about next 24 hours, answered truthfully |

**Aetheric Channels -- Weaving Reference**

*Full-caster Paths: Comet-Mage, Zodiac Priest, Resonance Seeker, Primal Accord. Half-caster: Oathed Vanguard, Scion-Pledged, Void-Hunter, Geode-Pilot, Coil-Stalker, Fade-Guardian. Quarter-caster: Fate-Breaker. Special: Star-Born (Surge Points = Depth), Ashé-Medium (Ashé Vessel), Rāśi-Siddha (Tapas), Accord-Maker (Infusions/Blueprints).*

| **Depth** | **1st** | **2nd** | **3rd** | **4th** | **5th** | **6th** | **7th** | **8th** | **9th** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1** | 2 | — | — | — | — | — | — | — | — |
| **2** | 3 | — | — | — | — | — | — | — | — |
| **3** | 4 | 2 | — | — | — | — | — | — | — |
| **4** | 4 | 3 | — | — | — | — | — | — | — |
| **5** | 4 | 3 | 2 | — | — | — | — | — | — |
| **6** | 4 | 3 | 3 | — | — | — | — | — | — |
| **7** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 1 | — | — | — | — | — |
| **8** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 2 | — | — | — | — | — |
| **9** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 3 | 1 | — | — | — | — |
| **10** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 3 | 2 | — | — | — | — |
| **11–12** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 3 | 2 | 1 | — | — | — |
| **13–14** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 3 | 2 | 1 | 1 | — | — |
| **15–16** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 3 | 2 | 1 | 1 | 1 | — |
| **17–20** | 4 | 3 | 3 | 3 | 2 | 1 | 1 | 1 | 1 |

| **Rule** | **Detail** |
| --- | --- |
| **Upcast** | Always expend a higher-tier Channel for a lower-tier Working. Effect does not increase unless Working description specifies Channel-tier scaling. |
| **Sustained Resonance** | Only ONE active at a time (unless a feat allows more). Maintaining costs no action. Ends on: new Sustained Working begun; unconscious; fail END Warding Resonance after damage; willingly end (free action). |
| **Weaving while threatened** | Does not provoke a Reflex Strike unless the Working requires physical movement through a creature's space. |
| **Stillness (Ore zones)** | All Weaving impossible. Channels cannot be expended. Resonance-Locked condition applies to all Weave-capable characters. |
| **Aetheric Depletion** | Pushing past Channels: gain 1 level per Channel forced. 5 levels = 1d10 psychic damage per Moment. Clears on Attunement. |

