| **✶  SIMPLE WEAPONS  ✶** **WEAPON** **DMG** **PROPERTIES** **RANGE** **COST** Club 1d4 B Light Melee 1 sm Dagger 1d4 P Finesse, Light, Thrown 20/60 ft 2 gm Greatclub 1d8 B Two-handed Melee 2 sm Handaxe 1d6 S Light, Thrown 20/60 ft 5 gm Quarterstaff 1d6 B Versatile (1d8) Melee 2 sm Spear 1d6 P Thrown, Versatile 20/60 ft 1 gm Light Crossbow 1d8 P Two-handed, Loading 80/320 ft 25 gm Shortbow 1d6 P Two-handed 80/320 ft 25 gm **✶  MARTIAL WEAPONS (KEY)  ✶** **WEAPON** **DMG** **PROPERTIES** **RANGE** **COST** Battleaxe 1d8 S Versatile (1d10) Melee 10 gm Glaive 1d10 S Heavy, Reach, 2H Melee 20 gm Greatsword 2d6 S Heavy, Two-handed Melee 50 gm Longsword 1d8 S Versatile (1d10) Melee 15 gm Rapier 1d8 P Finesse Melee 25 gm Scimitar 1d6 S Finesse, Light Melee 25 gm Shortsword 1d6 P Finesse, Light Melee 10 gm Hand Crossbow 1d6 P Light, Loading 30/120 ft 75 gm Longbow 1d8 P Heavy, Two-handed 150/600 ft 50 gm Warhammer 1d8 B Versatile (1d10) Melee 15 gm *B = Bludgeoning │ P = Piercing │ S = Slashing │ 2H = Two-handed │ Finesse = use SWI instead of FOR* **✶  SPECIAL MATERIALS  ✶** **MATERIAL** **PRICE** **NOTES** **Weep-Stone (3 charges)** 400 gm Each charge: -2 Lead-Scale Corruption; disrupts Void-Husk coordination for 1 Pulse; Kanya purification component. K'uh-la'an internal currency. **Black Iron** 80-120 gm/lb Not sold in standard markets — Dunmarim barter only. Retains full effectiveness in Stillness (Ore) zones. Only common weapon material unaffected by the Stillness. **Resonant Geode (Tier I)** ∼200 gm Powers Gear-Forged frames. Controlled by Geode-Pilot factions. Fully suppressed in Ore zones. **Resonant Geode (Tier III)** ∼2,000 gm 50% capacity in Ore zones. Required for advanced Gear-Forged function. **Moon-Petal Lotus** 800-1,200 gm Life-extending herb. K'uh-la'an’s highest-value trade good — given, not sold. Coil wants it for operative preservation. **Aether-Dampening Ore** 5,000+ gm Not sold openly. Dunmarim & Republic of Argentum control supply. Creates 30 ft Stillness zone per unit. The Coil deploys it tactically. | **✶  ARMOR ****&**** SHIELDS  ✶** **ARMOR** **GUARD RATING** **STEALTH** **MIN FOR** **COST** Padded (Light) 11+SWI Discord — 5 gm Leather (Light) 11+SWI — — 10 gm Studded Leather (Light) 12+SWI — — 45 gm Hide (Medium) 12+SWI max+2 — — 10 gm Chain Shirt (Medium) 13+SWI max+2 — — 50 gm Scale Mail (Medium) 14+SWI max+2 Discord — 50 gm Breastplate (Medium) 14+SWI max+2 — — 400 gm Chain Mail (Heavy) 16 Discord FOR 13 75 gm Splint (Heavy) 17 Discord FOR 15 200 gm Full Plate (Heavy) 18 Discord FOR 15 1,500 gm Standard Shield +2 GR — — 10 gm Tower Shield +3 GR — — 40 gm **✶  COST OF LIVING (PER DAY)  ✶** **LIFESTYLE** **COST** **PROVIDES** **Wretched** Free Sleeping rough. END Warding DC 10 weekly or gain Exhaustion L1 **Squalid** 1 sm Flophouse or stable. Adequate to survive **Poor** 5 sm Shared lodging, simple meals. Most laborers **Modest** 1 gm Private room, decent meals, stabling for a horse **Comfortable** 2 gm Good inn, quality food, minor luxuries **Wealthy** 4 gm Fine accommodation, servants available **Aristocratic** 10+ gm Private manor, personal staff, full social access **✶  KEY CONSUMABLES  ✶** **ITEM** **COST** **EFFECT** **Healing Draught (minor)** 50 gm Restores 2d4+2 Vitality. Drink as Instinct. **Healing Draught (greater)** 150 gm Restores 4d4+4 Vitality. Drink as Instinct. **Antidote** 50 gm Removes all Corrupted stacks (poison only). Fortune on END vs. poison for 1 hour. **Weep-Stone (3 charges)** 400 gm Each charge: -2 Lead-Scale / disrupts Void-Husks / Kanya component. **Smoke Pellet** 25 gm As Act, throw 20 ft: 10 ft heavily obscured area, 1 Pulse. **Tanglefoot Bag** 50 gm Strike Res. throw 10 ft: hit → SWI Warding DC 12 or Seized 1 min. **✶  DOWNTIME ACTIVITIES (KEY)  ✶** **Training (Discipline/Language/Weapon)** 250 gm + 250 days. Requires willing instructor. **Recuperating** 7 days. Removes 1 Exhaustion level. **Legendary Beast Vigil (your sign)** 2d4 weeks. Travel costs. Not guaranteed — the Beast chooses. **Kanya Siddha Purification** 1 hour; 50 gm/session. Removes 4 Lead-Scale Corruption levels (Stages 3–4). **Fated Bond Acknowledgment** 1 day, no cost. Both parties present. Advances bond tier. **Aetheric Research (Weave-capable)** 1+ weeks, 50 gm/week. Learn 1 Working or Lore item per week. **Faction Standing Work** 2+ weeks. Build standing with Kallos-Sworn, temples, lords, or Coil fronts. **Ceque Line Walking** 1 week/node, free. Blocked in Ore zones. Builds toward D8 Cross-Cultural Feat. |
